Sentencas: A direct carbon solid oxide fuel cell (DC-SOFC) stack was prepared with 3 tubular cells electrically connected in series.
Titulo: A High Performance Direct Carbon Solid Oxide Fuel Cell Stack for Portable Applications

Sentencas: To increase carbon storage in the stack, the anode was fabricated outside the tubular cells so that carbon fuel can be loaded at the exterior of the stack, which is more spacious than the interior.
Titulo: A High Performance Direct Carbon Solid Oxide Fuel Cell Stack for Portable Applications

Sentencas: The 3-cell-stack is operated directly with carbon as the fuel and oxygen in ambient air as the oxidant.
Titulo: A High Performance Direct Carbon Solid Oxide Fuel Cell Stack for Portable Applications

Sentencas: With a total effective area of 10.2 cm(2) and a 5% (w) Fe-loaded activated carbon fuel of 17 g, the stack reveals a peak power of 4.1 W at 800 degrees C.
Titulo: A High Performance Direct Carbon Solid Oxide Fuel Cell Stack for Portable Applications

Sentencas: The stack discharged at a constant current of 1.0 A for 19 h, giving a charge capacity of 19 A center dot h and an energy capacity of 31.6 W center dot h, which are much higher than those of a similar stack with anode on the inside and carbon loaded at the interior.
Titulo: A High Performance Direct Carbon Solid Oxide Fuel Cell Stack for Portable Applications

Sentencas: The high capacity of our DC-SOFC opens up potential applications in portable devices.
Titulo: A High Performance Direct Carbon Solid Oxide Fuel Cell Stack for Portable Applications
